        </h2>
        <div
          style="
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
          "
        >
          <a
            style="
              text-decoration: none;
              color: #333;
              display: block;
              background-color: #f9f9f9;
              padding: 20px;
